{"tid":29241,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人生若只如初見， 何事秋風悲畫扇？","createTime":"2016-12-08T12:21:05.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T09:02:14.000Z","uid":44209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c3175b9b5029fd64f23c0b4283f72a73a03c6935","tid":29241,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:21:06.000Z","msg":"如果可以時光倒流，番返去以前，你話幾好呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人生若只如初見，<br />\n何事秋風悲畫扇？<br />\n等閒變卻故人心，<br />\n卻道故人心易變。"},{"pid":"7aefae163bbf1585e2ce9a52e162918d5ebb0245","tid":29241,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:31:23.000Z","msg":"推薦巴打睇套戲 about time<br />\n無以前既你 就無而家既你"},{"pid":"9016263565dd12ac253b2ab761f1d7b775cecd62","tid":29241,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:43:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推薦巴打睇套戲 about time<br />\n無以前既你 就無而家既你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似好多劣評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a732533b047f029369e335706a1d24619e5282c","tid":29241,"uid":36909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:44:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"221ebd622ba11ed15d61541157e308ebc3c54157","tid":29241,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:45:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb08cae9ce94d1af51285bb34cd72903dfd3c28d","tid":29241,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:29:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea334c736fcf369cc1143b6e7fa6ea4a40f8bff4","tid":29241,"uid":10125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:30:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果可以時光倒流，番返去以前，你話幾好呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人生若只如初見，<br />\n何事秋風悲畫扇？<br />\n等閒變卻故人心，<br />\n卻道故人心易變。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人生最刺激嘅地方就係未知嘅結果<br />\n變左可以修補 唔試就乜都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3497857c8d6c5b8166844115e6a236eafe81ec09","tid":29241,"uid":55159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:33:17.000Z","msg":"不知道在那天邊可會有盡頭"},{"pid":"c82eba91e0375bd940dc96f8929c0cc9a1ac46d5","tid":29241,"uid":56210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:35:46.000Z","msg":"從今天開始相識當作別離時間就似活多一世紀&nbsp;"},{"pid":"ceb72ed24b0d3eb112130ca91ccb10858a5b608c","tid":29241,"uid":38744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:37:26.000Z","msg":"呢首真係好正"},{"pid":"5160cab83e34f9f9676272baf29fdaab2a124720","tid":29241,"uid":7721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:56:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果可以時光倒流，番返去以前，你話幾好呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人生若只如初見，<br />\n何事秋風悲畫扇？<br />\n等閒變卻故人心，<br />\n卻道故人心易變。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你要知道：<br />\n希望只不過是掩飾絕望的假面具，<br />\n然而人生空餘絕望那我亦何必珍惜。<br />\n得之，我幸；失之，我命。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc2a099f4e20f942d7ea42bbf5e414ef8576d219","tid":29241,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T14:40:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>推薦巴打睇套戲 about time<br />\n無以前既你 就無而家既你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似好多劣評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最後嗰part先係精髓 前面就好膠同好拖戲"},{"pid":"53194af67bd94e9b816699ab08b7338b8fd695f3","tid":29241,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T09:01:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果可以時光倒流，番返去以前，你話幾好呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人生若只如初見，<br />\n何事秋風悲畫扇？<br />\n等閒變卻故人心，<br />\n卻道故人心易變。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人生最刺激嘅地方就係未知嘅結果<br />\n變左可以修補 唔試就乜都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正因爲咁，人先會對將來/未知嘅嘢感到恐懼丶㥬惶。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有試做咗啲錯誤決定，真係好後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1719089563767041a3384ae0935f42e91a278aa2","tid":29241,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T09:01:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不知道在那天邊可會有盡頭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小鳳姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbd49a60f65db642ad149da8193f6f3b1e399340","tid":29241,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T09:02:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢首真係好正</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}